# Snort Fundamental
Snort is an open-source Network Instrusion Detection System (NIDS)

## Important directory
Configuration file are typically located in : /etc/snort

## Core components
- snort.conf (main configuration file)
- rules/ directory (contains detection rules)
- log directory (alerts and traffic logs)

Snort can run in:
- Sniffer mode
- Packet logger mode
- IDS mode
